title: Netflix's Holidate Part Two With 90 Day Gays
description:
**This episode also avail as video on Crappens On Demand http://bit.ly/crappensvideo**
We're back with Matt and Jake from the 90 Day Gays Podcast for part two of our Holidate recap. The final part will release tomorrow, and you can catch the video versions over at Crappens on Demand on Patreon. Find Matt and Jake at https://www.sissythattalk.com @90daygays @themattmarr @jakeitorfakeit

Our Patreon Extras: https://patreon.com/watchwhatcrappens
